Package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.output.ambassador

Class OutputGeneratorLoader

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.output.ambassador.OutputGeneratorLoader
Direct Known Subclasses:
FileOutputLoader, WebsocketVisualizerLoader
public abstract class OutputGeneratorLoader extends Object
A template class for runtime loadable output generators config classes, also serves as a factory for creating actual AbstractOutputGenerator instances).
